Preparation

qqpoint = function(qtl){
  m = qtl$cis
  cnts = m$hist.counts;
  bins = m$hist.bins;
  ntst = m$ntests;
  
  cusu = cumsum(cnts) / ntst;
  ypos = bins[-1][is.finite(cusu)];
  xpos = cusu[is.finite(cusu)];
  if(length(m$eqtls$pvalue)==0)
    return();
  ypvs = -log10(m$eqtls$pvalue);
  xpvs = -log10(1:length(ypvs) / ntst);
  if(length(ypvs) > 1000){
    # need to filter a bit, make the plotting faster
    levels = as.integer( xpvs/xpvs[1] * 1e3);
    keep = c(TRUE, diff(levels)!=0);
    levels = as.integer( ypvs/ypvs[1] * 1e3);
    keep = keep | c(TRUE, diff(levels)!=0);
    ypvs = ypvs[keep];
    xpvs = xpvs[keep];
    rm(keep)
  }
  return(data.frame(x = xpvs, y = ypvs));
}

# filtering
Gene_Total <- lapply(Gene_Total, function(x) {x[expected_count >= 6 & TPM >= 0.1, ]})
Gene_Total <- lapply(Gene_Total, function(x) {x[, gene_id:=substr(gene_id, 1, 15)]})
# Total_gene <- unique(substr(do.call(rbind, Gene_Total)[[1]], 1, 15))
stopifnot(identical(SampInfo_PolyA$donor_id, SampInfo_Total$donor_id))
Gene_TPM <- list()
for(i in 1:40){
  tmp <- merge(Gene_PolyA[[i]][, c(1, 3)], Gene_Total[[i]][, c(1, 3)], by = "gene_id")
  colnames(tmp)[2:3] <- c("PolyA", "Total")
  Gene_TPM[[i]] <- tmp
}

Mat <- rbind(data.frame(R = mapply(Gene_TPM, FUN = function(x) x[gene_id %in% substr(unique(RSEM_cis_tu[Type == "PolyA", gene]), 1, 15), cor(log1p(PolyA), log1p(Total))]), Type = "PolyA"),
             data.frame(R = mapply(Gene_TPM, FUN = function(x) x[gene_id %in% substr(unique(RSEM_cis_tu[Type == "Total", gene]), 1, 15), cor(log1p(PolyA), log1p(Total))]), Type = "Total"),
             data.frame(R = mapply(Gene_TPM, FUN = function(x) x[gene_id %in% substr(unique(RSEM_cis_tu[Type == "Common", gene]), 1, 15), cor(log1p(PolyA), log1p(Total))]), Type = "Common"))
library(ggpubr)
my_comparisons = list(c("PolyA", "Total"), c("Total", "Common"), c("PolyA", "Common"))
ggplot(Mat, aes(x = Type, y = R, fill = Type))+
  geom_violin(alpha = .5)+
  geom_boxplot(fill = "white", width = .2)+
  theme_classic() +
  theme(axis.title = element_text(size = 22), 
        axis.text = element_text(size = 16), 
        axis.title.x = element_blank())+
  ggbeeswarm::geom_quasirandom(size = 1, alpha = .5)+
  stat_compare_means(label = "p.format", comparisons = my_comparisons) +
  labs(title = "Correlation of TPM")
